OL,3,CMan convicted of manslaughter of 18-
OL,4,Cyear-old in Bournemouth following
OL,5,Cretrial
OL,7,FA 20-year-old man who stabbed an 18-
OL,8,Fyear-old in Bournemouth town centre
OL,9,Fhas been found guilty for the second
OL,10,Ftime of manslaughter after his
OL,11,Foriginal conviction was overturned on
OL,12,Fappeal.
OL,14,FA jury convicted Thomas Betteridge of
OL,15,Fmanslaughter and possessing a bladed
OL,16,Farticle in a public place in relation
OL,17,Fto the stabbing of Cameron Hamilton in
OL,18,Fthe early hours of August 5 2023.
