OL,3,CMan convicted of manslaughter of 18-
OL,4,Cyear-old in Bournemouth following
OL,5,Cretrial
OL,7,FHe was previously convicted of
OL,8,Fmanslaughter in March 2024 but the
OL,9,Fconviction was quashed leading to the
OL,10,Fretrial at Bournemouth Crown Court.
OL,12,FBetteridge will be sentenced on May 8.
OL,14,FJohn Price KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,15,Fretrial that during the incident,
OL,16,FBetteridge had been pushed into a bush
OL,17,Fby Mr Hamilton before the defendant
OL,18,Fthen stabbed him.
