OL,7,FHe said the defendant then ran away,
OL,8,Fleaving a trainer behind at the scene,
OL,9,Falong with a second teenager.
OL,11,FThe prosecutor said that Betteridge
OL,12,Fwas heard by a witness to say: "I
OL,13,Fsliced him up, I sliced him up" and
OL,14,Fadded that he had spoken the words
OL,15,F"almost in a boastful and proud
OL,16,Fmanner" and said that he was "laughing
OL,17,Fa little bit".
OL,19,FHe said that the second teenager also
OL,20,F"let out a childish giggle".
