OL,7,FMr Price said that Betteridge then
OL,8,Fchanged top and trainers with friends
OL,9,Fat the scene before he was stopped by
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FHe said that Betteridge expressed
OL,13,F"righteous indignation" at being
OL,14,Fstopped and searched by police, and
OL,15,Ffilmed the officers using his mobile
OL,16,Fphone before posting the video on
OL,17,FInstagram.
