OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Neil Third,
OL,8,Fof the Major Crime Investigation Team,
OL,9,Fsaid: "I hope this conviction offers
OL,10,Fsome comfort to Cameron's family, who
OL,11,Fhave continued to conduct themselves
OL,12,Fin a dignified and supportive manner
OL,13,Fthroughout the further court process
OL,14,Fthey have had to endure.
