OL,7,F"Despite the unimaginable grief they
OL,8,Fwill have experienced at losing their
OL,9,Floved one at such a young age, they
OL,10,Fhave continued to campaign to raise
OL,11,Fawareness of the tragic consequences
OL,12,Fof knife crime and made a real
OL,13,Fdifference in the local community
OL,14,Fthrough their Changes Are Made charity.
OL,16,F"We will continue to support them and
OL,17,Fwork with all our partners to raise
OL,18,Fawareness of knife crime and take
OL,19,Frobust action against offenders.
